  "keyFeatures": [
    "All data structures implemented from scratch without STL containers",
    "Role-based authentication system (Admin, Driver, Passenger)",
    "Trip lifecycle management using Queue (waiting), DoublyLinkedList (active), and Stack (history)",
    "Graph-based city routing with Dijkstra's shortest path algorithm",
    "AVL Tree for O(log n) range-based trip/driver queries",
    "Hash Table with chaining for O(1) average-case passenger and driver lookups",
    "Binary Search Tree for vehicle management ordered by license plate",
    "Multiple sorting algorithms: HeapSort, ShellSort, QuickSort, MergeSort, TimSort, CountingSort",
    "Binary search (iterative and recursive) with lambda comparator support",
    "File persistence: automatic save/load of passengers, drivers, trips, and admins"
  ],
